ycle guidance. The namespace migration is disruptive but does not constitute loss of capability (users can still run every command under the new prefix) — 'critical' reserves for capability loss, security, or data-loss consequences. The empty blocked-by list is accurate because both prerequisites (#114, #117) are status=complete; no active blocker exists."}], "status": "ok"}
